And I‚Äôm being accused of a horrible disgusting vile crime that I absolutely did not commit. I post my personal life and photos and happy moments on FB and IG. I am extremely sad and don‚Äôt know how to fix this. There‚Äôs no one to contact and no support. This is absurd and cruel.
